Definition: a toxic protein extracted from castor beans
Example: used as a chemical reagent; can be used as a bioweapon; one milligram of ricin can kill an adult
Synonyms: ricin_toxin, albumin, toxin, a, toxic, protein, extracted, from, castor, beans, used, as, chemical, reagent, can, be, bioweapon, one, milligram, of, kill, an, adult
Category: noun.substance
